    "(33)The real numbers tij and the phases ϕ ij are the analogous of sij and ϕ K,d,s in the quark sector: ( t12, ϕ 12) enter in µ → e transitions, ( t13, ϕ 13) in τ → e transitions, ( t23, ϕ 23) in τ → µ transitions.",
    "Also in this case ϵ 1,2 ̸ = 0 produces lepton flavour violating Z ′ interactions.• Neutrino couplings to Z ′:∆ ν i νi L = g Z ′ - 1 2 + ϵ i (i = ν 1, ν 2, ν 3).",
    "(34)Hence, after the fermion rotation from flavour to mass eigenstates, the free parameters in the model compriseg Z ′, M Z ′, ϵ 1, ϵ 2,(35)with ϵ 1,2 rational numbers, and the mixing angles and phases in the Z ′ couplings to righthanded fermions: (s 12, ϕ K), (s 13, ϕ d), (s 23, ϕ s) (36) for quarks, and ( t12, ϕ 12), ( t13, ϕ 13), ( t23, ϕ 23)for leptons.",
